T02TD1954E:80a-1: ho ma bi dhishti sha krishna ya m'a ri n'a ma /
T02TD1954E:80a-3: gshin rje gshed kyi ro sreg gi cho ga zhes bya ba //
T02TD1954E:80a-4: dpal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1954E:80a-5: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje can //
T02TD1954E:80a-6: zab mo bcas pa'i rdo rje ni //
T02TD1954E:80a-7: bla med snying po la btud de //
T02TD1954E:80a-8: ro sreg cho ga bshad par bya //
T02TD1954E:80a-9: sems can sangs rgyas snying po can //
T02TD1954E:80a-10: sangs rgyas nyid du rab sbyor ba'i //
T02TD1954E:80a-11: thabs kyi khyad par ro sreg par //
T02TD1954E:80a-12: rnam pa gnyis su shes bya ste //
T02TD1954E:80a-13: bsgrubs la bsreg par bya ba dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-14: dur khrod bsreg par bya ba'o //
T02TD1954E:80a-15: bsgrubs la bsreg pa rnam bzhi ste //
T02TD1954E:80a-16: dang por longs spyod 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-17: gnyis pa rab tu phye ba la //
T02TD1954E:80a-18: gsum pa nye ba'i sgrub pa nyid //
T02TD1954E:80a-19: bzhi pa mchod rten cho ga yi //
T02TD1954E:80a-20: dang po ro la khrus byas nas //
T02TD1954E:80a-21: bsrung ba'i cho ga rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-22: phyi yi gtor ma gtang bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80a-23: de nas tshogs bsags nas bzung ste //
T02TD1954E:80a-24: mngon par rtogs pa rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-25: bzang po'i khri la bzhag nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80a-26: rgyan gyis legs par spras pa la //
T02TD1954E:80a-27: ga pur la sogs khar blud nas //
T02TD1954E:80a-28: bdud rtsir byin gyis brlab bya ste //
T02TD1954E:80a-29: snying gar gzungs thag btags nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80a-30: rtsa ba'i sngags la de nyid gsum //
T02TD1954E:80a-31: spel ba'i bzlas pa khri tsam bya //
T02TD1954E:80a-32: de nas bye brag las byas nas //
T02TD1954E:80a-33: thod pa klad pa dbang po lnga //
T02TD1954E:80a-34: snying sogs bzhi dang nyva bzhi dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-35: snum dang bdud rtsi lnga dang gnas //
T02TD1954E:80a-36: rkang brgyang sde ba'i bu ga dgu //
T02TD1954E:80a-37: rgyas pa'i srad bus bcings nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80a-38: shun pa'i nang du dril la bzhag / de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa ni //
T02TD1954E:80a-39: rtog pa dang bcas rtog med dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-40: shin tu rtog med la sogs ni //
T02TD1954E:80a-41: gang zag sems kyi khyad par yin //
T02TD1954E:80a-42: de yang rab tu sbyar ba dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-43: 'dod pa gzhan la spel ba dang //
T02TD1954E:80a-44: rtog med rlon pa'i rol ba'o //
T02TD1954E:80b-0: de nas tshogs @80b kyi 'khor lo las //
T02TD1954E:80b-1: byung ba'i bkra shis smon btab nas //
T02TD1954E:80b-2: tshe las 'das pa'i don gyi phyir //
T02TD1954E:80b-3: bsngo ba rab tu zin par bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-5: smon lam dkyil 'khor de nyid dang //
T02TD1954E:80b-6: lha yi de nyid las sbyar ba'i //
T02TD1954E:80b-7: tshe las 'das pa'i don gyi phyir //
T02TD1954E:80b-8: rgya chen rab tu gdab par bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-9: sbyang ba gsum du shes bya ste //
T02TD1954E:80b-10: dang po thal ba btags la btsag / de nas dri dang sbyar bya ste //
T02TD1954E:80b-11: hr'i: shtri: la ni ngan 'gro kun //
T02TD1954E:80b-12: sbyong bar byed pa'i sngags btags la //
T02TD1954E:80b-13: khri'am stong du bzlas pa bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-14: de nas mandala ngos mnyam la //
T02TD1954E:80b-15: ba yi rnam lngas byugs nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80b-16: dri zhim pa yi bsgos pa'i sa //
T02TD1954E:80b-17: dri yis thig le gdab par bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-18: de nas srog chags med 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1954E:80b-19: mnyen zhing 'jam la dkar ba'i sa //
T02TD1954E:80b-20: blangs la dri zhim chu yis bran //
T02TD1954E:80b-21: de nas thal ba dang bsres la //
T02TD1954E:80b-22: 'jim pa legs pa'i gong bu bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-23: de nas snying ga'i sa bon las //
T02TD1954E:80b-25: 'og gi gnas nas bkug byas la /
T02TD1954E:80b-26: lus ngag yid gsum sbyang ba bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-27: de nas h'um h'um zhes brjod pas //
T02TD1954E:80b-28: khu ba'i thig ler zhu gyur te //
T02TD1954E:80b-29: aa dkar thung du gsal bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-31: dbyangs dang gsal yig bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-32: de las rdo rjer gyur nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80b-33: h'um gis mtshan pa las 'phros pa'i //
T02TD1954E:80b-34: phyag rgya'i tshogs rnams bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-35: de nas rang gi lha dang ni //
T02TD1954E:80b-36: yang na rdo rje sems dpa' ru //
T02TD1954E:80b-37: bskyed la sku rnams bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-38: de yang byin gyis brlab pa ni //
T02TD1954E:80b-39: aom sarba ta th'a ga t'a k'a ya badzra sra bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1954E:80b-40: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta w'a ka badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1954E:80b-41: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta tsatta badzra svabh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1954E:80b-42: de nas byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags //
T02TD1954E:80b-43: nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas byas la //
T02TD1954E:80b-44: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstims nas kyang //
T02TD1954E:80b-45: 'od kyi phung por blta bar bya //
T02TD1954E:80b-46: de nas rten 'brel ldan pa'i sngags //
T02TD1954E:80b-47: brjod cing btab la 'khor lo bsgom //
T02TD1954E:80b-48: sngon gyi mandala drang ba'i dkyil //
T02TD1954E:80b-49: dri yi thig les brgyan pa la //
T02TD1954E:80b-50: me tog tshom bu bkod pa'i steng //
T02TD1954E:80b-51: spyan drangs nas ni bzhugs su gsol //
T02TD1954E:80b-52: de nas 'khor lo rgyal mtshan dang //
T02TD1954E:80b-53: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan 'phen gyis brgyan //
T02TD1954E:80b-54: de nas na bza' dkar po gsol //
T02TD1954E:80b-55: bkod pa shin tu mdzes byas la //
T02TD1954E:81a-2: dgug gzhug mchod dang bstod byas la //
T02TD1954E:81a-3: bdud rtsi myang dang spro bsdu bzlas //
T02TD1954E:81a-4: rdzogs nas bsngo dang smon lam btab //
T02TD1954E:81a-5: de nas gzhal yas bzang po'i nang //
T02TD1954E:81a-6: bzhugs su gsol la rtag tu mchod //
T02TD1954E:81a-7: ro bsregs pa'i rus pa'i s'a tstsha'i cho ga yin //
T02TD1954E:81a-8: gshin rje gshed kyi ro sreg gi cho ga zhes bya ba slob dpon nag po zhabs kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
